issue.title: Xcode updates
issue.body:
I don't want to spend much time on this project, but I do want to keep it up to date with current tools so that we can deploy any fixes quickly. 

I tried updating to CocoaPods 1.0, but things went quickly awry. It's a large job, but not necessary for now.

pr.title: Xcode updates
